      • getAllFields

        public java.util.List getAllFields()
        Return a List of SA Fields for all the java fields in this class, including all inherited fields. This includes hidden fields. Thus the returned list can contain fields with the same name. Return an empty list if there are no fields. Only designed for use in a debugging system.
